smashbroshaxer
================

simple script that aids in executing smashbroshax under Linux.

Requirements:
* Linux (x86/x86_64)
* Gtk+ 3
* sudo

Usage:
* run script in terminal
* select wifi device
* select game version
* press hax
* [if requested] enter your password in terminal
* in game go to Smash > Group
* ... profit?
